		<tr valign=top>
			<td class="BoardRowB" colspan=2 width="83%">
				For the stat question: <br>  <br> INT <br> DEX <br> STR(if you want to carry extra loot only) <br>  <br> The rest really doesn't matter and I would honestly say that STR isn't really important either. <br>  <br> As for the spec, I wouldn't really suggest the Servant spec unless you have a BuffBot.  If you do, great.  If not go with 48Si/24Se for farming purposes.  50Sight is more of an RvR spec and while you can still farm you will miss out on the 24 Damage Shield.
